 IT WAS A GAME, A VERY INTERESTING GAME ONE COULD
 PLAY.  WHENEVER ONE SOLVED ONE OF THE LITTLE PROBLEMS,
 ONE COULD WRITE A PAPER ABOUT IT.  IT WAS VERY EASY IN
 THOSE DAYS FOR ANY SECOND-RATE PHYSICIST TO DO
